results.title: College Closures due to COVID-19
results.snippet:
Survey to generate data for a map of college closures due to the COVID-19 outbreak.
If you'd like to add a school:
1. Please check that the school you're adding is not already in the list. Some schools have common alternate names (ie, CU Boulder is really the University of Colorado - Boulder)
2. Fill in as much info as you can about the closure: School name, city, state, details of impact, dates of impact, link to more info.

Thank you for your participation!
Created by Elizabeth Tulanowski, Colorado State University GIS Instructor
